  <summary date="2004-06-09T19:21:37Z" status="Introduced in House">Federal Disaster Consumer Protection Act - Amends the Fair Credit Reporting Act to prohibit a consumer reporting agency from making any consumer report containing any reference to a late payment that was due solely to a disruption caused by a declared disaster for which the agency received specified notice.

Sets forth procedures for striking adverse information due to declared disasters.</summary>
